WEBVTT

00:00:30.351 --> 00:00:33.153
But it is nearly impossible

00:00:33.177 --> 00:00:36.652
for an American to get discharged
their student loan debts.

00:00:40.421 --> 00:00:43.141
Once upon a time in America,

00:00:43.165 --> 00:00:45.815
going to college did not mean
graduating with debt.

00:00:47.299 --> 00:00:52.585
My friend Paul's father
graduated from Colorado State University

00:00:52.609 --> 00:00:53.759
on the GI Bill.

00:00:55.546 --> 00:00:57.134
For his generation,

00:00:57.158 --> 00:01:00.006
higher education was free or almost free,